name: ✴ 𝕸𝖎𝖓𝖉𝖑𝖊𝖘𝖘 ✴
description:
✴ Portrait of Mindless

The Mind is full of stars, however, the unbreakable glass does not let any sparkle out. The Mind then became Mindless, blind and muted to the world.  

✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consist of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
